import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    genus_count = data.groupby('Genus').size().reset_index(name='count')
    plt.bar(genus_count['Genus'], genus_count['count'])
    plt.title('What is the distribution of bacteria based on their genus?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.scatter(data['Penicillin'], data['Streptomycin'])
    ax.set_xlabel('Penicillin')
    ax.set_ylabel('Streptomycin')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between Penicillin and Streptomycin?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data = data[['Neomycin', 'Gram_Staining']]
    chart = data.boxplot(by='Gram_Staining', column='Neomycin', figsize=(10,6))
    chart.set_xlabel('Gram Staining')
    chart.set_ylabel('Neomycin')
    chart.set_title('What is the distribution of Neomycin across different Gram Staining types?')
    chart.axhline(y=data['Neomycin'].median(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Neomycin'].median()))
    chart.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Streptomycin'] = pd.to_numeric(data['Streptomycin'], errors='coerce')
    gram_staining_types = data['Gram_Staining'].unique()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    for gram_staining_type in gram_staining_types:
        ax.hist(data[data['Gram_Staining'] == gram_staining_type]['Streptomycin'], alpha=0.5, label=gram_staining_type)
    ax.axvline(data['Streptomycin'].median(), color='k', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Streptomycin'].median()))
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Streptomycin across different Gram Staining types?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

    for gram_staining_type in gram_staining_types:
        ax.hist(data[data['Gram_Staining'] == gram_staining_type]['Streptomycin'], alpha=0.5, label=gram_staining_type)
    ax.axvline(data['Streptomycin'].median(), color='k', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['Streptomycin'].median()))
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of Streptomycin across different Gram Staining types?', wrap=True)
    return plt;
